# Xcode / Swift — https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Swift.gitignore

## Build artifacts
build/
DerivedData/
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.dSYM.zip
*.dSYM

## Xcode user state (per-developer, not shared)
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
.swiftpm/

## macOS
.DS_Store

## CocoaPods / Carthage (not used, but ignore if ever added)
Pods/
Carthage/Build/

## fastlane (not used)
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/screenshots/**/*.png

# App Store preview videos (regenerate via simctl + ffmpeg; large binaries)
AppStore/*.mp4
AppStore/*.mov
